snippet.title: Bot Rods Gameplay Trailer #01
snippet.description:
Wishlist us on Steam.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/913730/Bot_Rods/

Bot Rods is a family-friendly arcade style racing game with adorable characters and bots, racing around a futuristic world. Use power-ups, weapons & shortcuts to pilot your way to the top.
Feel free to ram your opponent into a barricade while you are at it.

BOT- SET- GO!!
